Áno?

18
00:03:00,410 --> 00:03:02,380
Si doma?

19
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:05,150
Ako sa má mama?

20
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:07,920
Vravela, že je v poriadku.

21
